object.customQuery:
SELECT PSS.PolicyNumber, PSS.PolicyVersion, PSS.RiskCd, PSS.CoverageCd, PSS.EffectiveDt, PSS.ExpirationDt, PSS.ReportPeriod, 
case when ltrim(rtrim(FeeCd)) in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee','NYFFFee') then 0 else PSS.MTDWrittenPremiumAmt end as MTDWrittenPremiumAmt,
case when ltrim(rtrim(FeeCd)) in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee','NYFFFee') then 0 else PSS.YTDWrittenPremiumAmt end as YTDWrittenPremiumAmt, 
case when ltrim(rtrim(FeeCd)) in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee','NYFFFee') then 0 else PSS.InforceAmt end  as InforceAmt,
case when ltrim(rtrim(FeeCd)) in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee','NYFFFee') then 0 else PSS.MTDEarnedPremiumAmt end as MTDEarnedPremiumAmt, 
case when ltrim(rtrim(FeeCd)) in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee','NYFFFee') then 0 else PSS.YTDEarnedPremiumAmt end as YTDEarnedPremiumAmt, 
PSS.TransactionCd, PSS.MajorPerilCd, PSS.ProducerCd, 
case when ltrim(rtrim(FeeCd)) in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee','NYFFFee') then 0 else PSS.UnearnedAmt end as UnearnedAmt, 
PSS.PolicyRef, PSS.UpdateDt,
 PSS.MTDWrittenCommissionAmt,
 PSS.YTDWrittenCommissionAmt,
 PSS.MTDWrittenCommissionFeeAmt, PSS.YTDWrittenCommissionFeeAmt, 
PSS.MTDWrittenPremiumFeeAmt, PSS.YTDWrittenPremiumFeeAmt, 
case when ltrim(rtrim(FeeCd)) in ('HealthyHomesFundFee', 'NJGFFee','NYFFFee') then 0 else PSS.MonthUnearnedAmt end as MonthUnearnedAmt,
 PSS.AnnualStatementLineCd, PSS.StatLineCd,
PSS.ClassCd,
PSS.TransactionNumber,RateAreaName
FROM
 dbo.POLICYSUMMARYSTATS_STG PSS
order by policynumber, policyversion

object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT Coverage.CoverageId as CoverageId, Coverage.PolicyKey as PolicyKey, Coverage.CoverageSystemId as CoverageSystemId, Coverage.CoverageCd as CoverageCd 
FROM dbo.Coverage 
JOIN dbo.policysummarystats_stg ps 
ON Coverage.CoverageSystemId = ps.policyref 
where Coverage.RowEffEndDt='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
and Coverage.RiskId is NULL
AND Coverage.PolicyKey IS NOT NULL 
ORDER BY Coverage.PolicyKey
--

object.customQuery:
select DISTINCT CoverageId as CoverageId,
PolicyKey as PolicyKey,
CoverageSystemId as CoverageSystemId,
CoverageCd as CoverageCd,
RiskId as RiskId
from
(
SELECT Coverage.CoverageId as CoverageId, 
Coverage.PolicyKey as PolicyKey, 
Coverage.CoverageSystemId as CoverageSystemId, 
Coverage.CoverageCd as CoverageCd, 
Coverage.RiskId as RiskId,
rank() over (partition by Coverage.PolicyKey, Coverage.CoverageSystemId, Coverage.CoverageCd, Coverage.RiskID order by Coverage.CoveragePremiumAmt Desc, Coverage.CoverageId, Coverage.CoverageStatus) as CoverageItemCd
FROM dbo.Coverage
JOIN dbo.policysummarystats_stg ps 
ON Coverage.CoverageSystemId = ps.policyref
AND Coverage.CoverageCd = ps.coveragecd
where RowEffEndDt='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
) sub
where CoverageItemCd = 1 
ORDER BY PolicyKey
---
